    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,47)
    # lpdcat normal "「啊……這個沒關係啦，我再去解釋一下就好了嘛。不用擔心，沒問題的！」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,47)
    lpdcat normal "\"Really... It doesn't matter. I'll clear things up, no problem at all!\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:500
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_64249b4b:

    # avt "「哪裡沒問題啊！學長你這樣解釋別人怎麼會信……而且學長你平常不會這麼做的啊，你到底是怎麼了？」"
    avt "\"No problem?! What in the world could you say to explain that! ...You weren't like this before. What the hell's wrong with you Senpai?\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:502
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_2eb346dd:

    # avt "「從清明連假之後，我就覺得你怪怪的。到底發生了什麼事？你跟我說清楚好不好？」"
    avt "\"Ever since you came back after the Ching Ming break I've felt like somethings been wrong. What happened? I care about you! Please, tell me everything!\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:506
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_b7b0a689:

    # b "在吵雜的電玩場中，即使我稍微加大音量，也不會被人注意。我把學長拉到角落。"
    b "My raised voice blends into background of the noisy arcade. I take Senpai and pull him into a nearby corner. "

# game/script/12.rpy:510
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_21d240af:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,48)
    # lpdcat difficult "「哪、哪有啊。是阿遼想太多了啦，我只是，嗯，因為要離開阿遼有點心情不好而已。沒什麼大不了的啦！」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,48)
    lpdcat difficult "\"Wha— What are you talking about? Liao, you're overreacting. I'm... well, I'm just upset over leaving. It's no big deal!\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:512
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_0c630fde:

    # avt "「我怎麼覺得不是這樣？而且學長這幾天的舉動都很奇怪啊。」"
    avt "\"Really, I don't think so. The past few day's you've been {i}different{/i}.\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:514
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_bffdc448:

    # avt "「這幾天你都不怎麼來找我，就算是考試週，我也覺得有點太少了。但今天又特地約我出來……剛剛還說什麼要離開，怎麼想都不對。」"
    avt "\"To begin with, you haven't even been really trying to come and spend time with me. Sure, it's exam week but it's not that hard.\" "
    avt "\"Then yesterday you straight up asked to go out with me out of the blue... Now you're telling me you might be leaving. It doesn't make sense.\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:516
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_908dbbd3:

    # avt "「我不知道這個離開，是石虎的你要離開還是書齊學長要離開，但不管是哪一個，之後書齊學長都不會跟我交往才對。」"
    avt "\"I don't know whether it's you or Shu-chi that's leaving. But no matter who it is, you won't be able to date me.\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:518
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_76bf23a7:

    # avt "「但你卻找我來這種有很多社員出沒的地方，還用那種招人誤會的方式把人趕走。學長你那麼聰明，應該不會沒考慮到這些事情啊……」"
    avt "\"You took me to a place that's specifically popular among the guys at dance club then made a show over kicking out one of your admirers in a way that {i}everyone's{/i} \ going to misunderstand.\" "
    avt "\"Senpai, I know you're smart enough to have thought this through...\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:523
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_f5ada393:

    # avt "「學長，如果你不是故意做這種事……」"
    avt "\"If you really did this on purpose...\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:526
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_6768f5e6:

    # avt "「那肯定有什麼隱情。告訴我好嗎？」" with vshake
    avt "\"Something must be up! Please tell me!\" " with vshake

# game/script/12.rpy:528
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_8a1f18a5:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,49)
    # lpdcat difficult "「阿遼……」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,49)
    lpdcat difficult "\"Liao...\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:532
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_f9afad63:

    # b "學長避開我的視線。"
    b "Senpai avoids my eyes. "

# game/script/12.rpy:534
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_8febc97b:

    # avt "「雖然……我沒有答應跟學長交往，也沒辦法陪你去苗栗，好像沒有資格問這些……可是你跑來我家也一個多月了，我們也不能算不熟，要是你要離開，我希望至少跟我說一下是怎麼了……」"
    avt "\"I'm not in a relationship with Senpai, and I can't go to Miaoli with you... So maybe I don't have the right to ask this from you...\" "
    avt "\"But you {i}lived{/i} \ in my home for over a month. I'd hope that we're at least close enough for you to tell me. If you are leaving, I'd like to know why...\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:541
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_554e93ce:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,50)
    # lpdcat difficult "「我……對不起阿遼，我也不是不願意告訴你，只是……」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,50)
    lpdcat difficult "\"I— Sorry, Liao. It's not that I don't want to tell you. Just...\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:543
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_c4a1d29c:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,51)
    # lpdcat difficult "「我不希望因為這些，變成好像你非來苗栗幫我不可。我的事情我想自己解決……」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,51)
    lpdcat difficult "\"I don't want to force you to go to Miaoli with me... I can take care of my own \nbusiness.\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:545
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_b4029453:

    # avt "「所以到底是什麼事？」"
    avt "\"Still, I want to know.\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:547
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_8a637f9f:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,52)
    # lpdcat serious "「……要說也可以啦，不過阿遼要答應我一件事喔。」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,52)
    lpdcat serious "\"Ok... I'll tell you. Just, promise me one thing.\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:549
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_8a16379d:

    # avt "「什麼事？」"
    avt "\"Name it.\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:551
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_3bcfbc99:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,53)
    # lpdcat serious "「不要因為我說的話而改變要不要來的決定。可以的話最好聽完後忘掉。雖然阿遼能不能來問題其實在阿遼的老家啦……」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,53)
    lpdcat serious "\"Don't let what I tell you change your decision on helping me. It'd be best to forget what I say right away if you can. I know that you coming or not depends on your family back home...\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:553
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_8ff96d9a:

    # avt "「老家那邊我再想辦法。但不管怎麼說，我想知道狀況……」"
    avt "\"I'll work on it. No matter what, I want to know what's going on...\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:559
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_a8e5a40f:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,54)
    # lpdcat normal "「嗯。其實也沒什麼大不了的。」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,54)
    lpdcat normal "\"Well. It's not a big deal.\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:561
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_70df493b:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,55)
    # lpdcat serious "「就是我家福德差不多快要神力散盡了。所以在最後的時間，我想回去陪陪祂，這樣而已。」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,55)
    lpdcat serious "\"It's just that it won't be too long until my Fudegong looses the last of his divine power. I want to be there with him in his last days. That's all.\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:563
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_f51f0117:

    # avt "「……神力散盡會怎樣？」"
    avt "\"...What's going to happen to him?\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:566
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_821c84a2:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,56)
    # lpdcat difficult "「就會……嗯……降階成{font=tl/None/NotoSansCJKtc-Bold.otf}地靈{/font}那種感覺吧？雖然不是不存在了，但會失去神格，沒辦法對話了。沒有人認為那片土地的神是個土地公，所以就無法維持土地公的形象。雖然只要有人祭拜的話還是有機會復原……」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,56)
    lpdcat difficult "\"They will... umm... degrade to an {font=tl/None/NotoSansCJKtc-Bold.otf}earth spirit{/font}, maybe.\" "
    lpdcat difficult "\"They'll still be around somewhere even if he looses his godship, they just won't {i}exist{/i} \ anymore... After all, a God of Soil doesn't exist if no one believes they do.\" "
    lpdcat difficult "\"One day they might recover if someone goes to worship them though.\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:568
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_a0229d08:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,57)
    # lpdcat difficult "「不過，就算復原，可能也不會有之前的記憶……」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,57)
    lpdcat difficult "\"But, even if they do come back, they'll probably end up losing all their memories...\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:570
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_c6c6a398:

    # b "也就是說，會忘記學長嗎？"
    b "In other words, his Fudegong will have forgotten all about him? "

# game/script/12.rpy:574
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_30dcc94e:

    # avt "「那你呢？你會怎樣？」"
    avt "\"What about you? What will happen to you?\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:576
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_e964a9d9:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,58)
    # lpdcat normal "「就變回妖怪嘍。不用擔心啦，變回妖怪也不會因此就性格大變什麼的。我還是我，只是不再是土地公的從祀神而已了。嗯——就好像公司倒閉了那樣？」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,58)
    lpdcat normal "\"I'll turn back to a yaoguai. Don't worry, it won't change who I am. I just won't be a guardian tiger anymore.\" "
    lpdcat normal "\"Hmm... It's kind of like a company going bankrupt, isn't it? The boss takes the fall while everyone else goes their separate ways.\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:578
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_1ddcc1a3:

    # avt "「可是你不是說復興廟宇可能會花上好幾年嗎？怎麼會那麼快土地公就要消逝了？」"
    avt "\"If it'd take us years to restore the temple, then how come it's got this bad so rapidly?\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:580
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_01be4d96:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,59)
    # lpdcat serious "「要讓廟宇穩定獲得信仰要一兩年，不過只要有廟公、有人整理廟宇的話，土地公就能維持形象啦。」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,59)
    lpdcat serious "\"I'd say it takes about two years for a temple to gain a stable following. But as long as there's a priest taking care of the temple it's not hard to maintain.\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:582
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_ec29959e:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,60)
    # lpdcat serious "「畢竟一個乾乾淨淨的廟跟荒廢的廟還是差很多的，只要有人看到，就算沒有來參拜，也會認為這座廟裡有土地公。光是這樣就很有幫助了呢。」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,60)
    lpdcat serious "\"After all there's a huge difference between a neglected temple and an deserted one. People think about it whether they want to pray or not. If they see someone there they'll assume the temple has an active god.\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:584
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_0c5e9592:

    # avt "「也就是說只要我過去，土地公就不會消逝了？」"
    avt "\"So as long as I'm there, the local God of Soil won't vanish?\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:586
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_ad91d9c4:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,61)
    # lpdcat serious "「是這樣說沒錯啦。」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,61)
    lpdcat serious "\"Pretty much.\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:588
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_2ecb157d:

    # avt "「……大概還有多久？」"
    avt "\"...How much time do we have?\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:590
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_915d1c0c:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,62)
    # lpdcat difficult "「這我也不敢說耶，不過真的是很危險了，我想最多應該沒辦法拖超過一個月吧。所以我大概這幾天就會回去了……」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,62)
    lpdcat difficult "\"I'm not sure. It's... getting close. Probably a month at most. So yeah, I'll have to go back in the next few days...\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:592
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_21765059:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,63)
    # lpdcat serious "「我知道阿遼在想什麼啦，不過沒辦法拖到暑假呢。要阿遼在學期結束前，放棄期末考跑去苗栗……我也覺得不可能呢。所以這樣的話，我想說不如……就到此為止了吧？」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,63)
    lpdcat serious "\"I know you wanted to wait until summer break, but that can't happen. I don't expect you to give up your finals just to come with me. So... It's better we stop here.\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:596
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_2501d905:

    # avt "「什麼到此為止？」" with vshake
    avt "\"Stop here?\" " with vshake

# game/script/12.rpy:598
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_5df6a53c:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,64)
    # lpdcat normal "「就是，我給阿遼造成的麻煩呀。這樣的話那個大叔也會開心了吧？」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,64)
    lpdcat normal "\"I've... just caused you trouble Liao. Even the old man would be happy to see me go.\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:601
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_954be41a:

    # avt "「哪有這樣的啊！」" with vshake
    avt "\"That's not true!\" " with vshake

# game/script/12.rpy:603
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_87c350e9:

    # avt "「這幾天就要走？這也太突然了……你家土地公已經快消散了，這麼重要的事怎麼不先跟我說？」"
    avt "\"You really have to go so soon? That's so sudden... Your God of Soil is almost gone. {i}Why{/i} \ did you keep this from me?\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:605
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_98ad3753:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,65)
    # lpdcat normal "「說了的話阿遼就能排除萬難過來嗎？」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,65)
    lpdcat normal "\"If I said so earlier, would that have changed anything? Would you have come to Miaoli with me?\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:607
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_2166e7b1:

    # avt "「……」"
    avt "\"......\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:613
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_adb3d9b5:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,66)
    # lpdcat normal "「對吧，所以我也不想用那種方式給你壓力。要是我一見到你馬上說『沒時間了立刻跟我來！』你肯定也不樂意吧。」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,66)
    lpdcat normal "\"See. I didn't want to put you under more pressure.\" "
    lpdcat normal "\"What? You want me to remind you every day? \"We're running out of time Liao!\" Oh, I'm {i}sure{/i} \ that would have been better.\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:615
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_645c6577:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,67)
    # lpdcat difficult "「而且在這次清明連假之前……老實說我雖然有顏書齊的記憶，但是很多事真的沒有親身體會不知道呢。我也是這一次才知道跟家人對抗有多麼困難……」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,67)
    lpdcat difficult "\"And honestly, I did change. Before Ching Ming, sure I {i}had{/i} \ Yan Shu-chi's memories but that didn't mean I {i}felt{/i} \ them. I didn't understand how much family meant... The pressures you're under.\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:617
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_fadb3e27:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,68)
    # lpdcat difficult "「阿遼家裡也是傳承了好幾代吧？這樣的話要阿遼突然離開就很困難，這已經不是阿遼自己的問題了……我注意到這一點，才發現我的要求有多為難阿遼……」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,68)
    lpdcat difficult "\"Your family's carried on that temple for generations, right? I can't just expect you to pack up your ancestry and leave.\" "
    lpdcat difficult "\"This isn't your problem and I shouldn't expect to make it yours... I've— I've just made things hard for Liao... That's all I've done...\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:619
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_2c8d50dc:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,69)
    # lpdcat difficult "「顏書齊跟家裡也是關係很差，這次清明連假吵得特別嚴重。我打算趁這個機會，接下來讓顏書齊請幾天的假，回去跟家裡好好談談。而我也就在那時候離開了吧。」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,69)
    lpdcat difficult "\"Yan Shu-chi's family— they really don't like him. We really didn't get along during the break. So, I'm gonna use this as a chance to have Yan Shu-chi talk things over with his family for a few days. Then I'll be free to leave.\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:621
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_362f2912:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,70)
    # lpdcat difficult "「對不起阿遼，沒有先跟你說就擅自決定了。但既然是否來苗栗不是你可以決定的，我也不想跟你說這些造成你的負擔……就想說慢慢退出比較好……」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,70)
    lpdcat difficult "\"I'm sorry Liao. I know I didn't talk to you before making this decision. But it's not like you being able to come to Miaoli is really your decision anyway.\" "
    lpdcat difficult "\"I don't want to burden you anymore... It's better to just slowly fade away from your life...\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:625
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_e38f6a3f:

    # avt "「那為什麼今天要和我約會？」"
    avt "\"Then why did you want to go on a date today?\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:627
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_6b1d08cc:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,71)
    # lpdcat wronged "「……畢竟要走了嘛。我希望最後跟阿遼道別前，至少能讓阿遼開心一點……」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,71)
    lpdcat wronged "\"I'm leaving... So I might as well try to give you a nice day to remember me by...\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:629
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_2166e7b1_1:

    # avt "「……」"
    avt "\"......\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:631
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_c5e973cd:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,72)
    # lpdcat serious "「阿遼，怎麼了……？」"
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,72)
    lpdcat serious "\"Liao... you okay?\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:635
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_3b20f0de:

    # avt "「學長……你覺得這樣就好嗎？」"
    avt "\"Senpai... Do you {i}really{/i} \ think this is good for either of us?\" "

# game/script/12.rpy:638
translate english cg_cat_play_dancing_machine_da4b6372:

    # voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,73)
    # lpdcat not_reconcile "「……當然不好啊！可是我有什麼辦法？我不能留更久，阿遼也不能來陪我。那我也只能……」" with hshake
    voice voice_file.lpdcat(12,73)
    lpdcat not_reconcile "\"...Of course it isn't! What else can I do? I can't stay here any longer. Liao can't come with me... S-{w=0.2}So I have to...\" " with hshake

# game/script/12.rpy:642
